commit 2db2f4f104a6e0ef2b02036feea2af41f0d01760
Author: dowiyogo <dowiyogo@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Jun 18 08:37:01 2026 +0200

    fix(optics): replace reflector volumes with bar skin surface
    
    Remove thin air-filled reflector sibling volumes that caused
    post-reflection optical-photon steps in the scintillator to be timed
    with the air group velocity.
    
    Apply the existing branch-specific reflector optical properties as a
    G4LogicalSkinSurface on the scintillator logical volume while
    preserving explicit bar-to-SiPM border surfaces.
    
    This prevents reflector-volume touchable aliasing in G4Transportation
    and keeps post-bounce timing at the scintillator GROUPVEL.
    
    (cherry picked from commit f39b84cb1396c66bf70897aefb10d16675fba11d)

